snippet.title: Galaxy on Fire 3 (Offical Store Trailer)
snippet.description:
Galaxy on Fire 3 is OUT NOW on Google Play and the App Store! 

Show your piloting skills in fierce space battles on the outskirts of the universe & take down the galaxy's most wanted criminals in explosive dogfights!

The pioneering sci-fi shooter on mobile returns with Galaxy on Fire 3. Take course for the far-off Neox Sector and face ruthless crime lords and their devoted legions of underlings.
